-- EON Job Cuts Will Save ‘Thousands’ Others, Teyssen Tells FAS
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2011-12-18T14:28:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-18/eon-job-cuts-will-save-thousands-others-teyssen-tells-fas.html
EON AG ’s plan to cut as many as
11,000 jobs are necessary to save “thousands” of other
positions, Chief Executive Officer Johannes Teyssen told the
 Frankfurter Allgemeine Sonntagszeitung  newspaper.  The job cuts are aimed at making  Germany ’s biggest utility
“agile and competitive,” Teyssen told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
